                <!-- ============ BOTTOM TAKEAWAY ============ -->
                <mxCell id="TAKE" value="&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:14px;&#39;&gt;🎯 TAKEAWAY&lt;/b&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Khác biệt nằm ở &lt;b&gt;Memory profile&lt;/b&gt;: Cách 1 → RAM = O(n) (phình to · OOM) &amp;nbsp; · &amp;nbsp; Cách 2 → RAM = O(1) (cố định · scale vô tận). &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Production rule of thumb: data &lt; 10k rows dùng cách 1 cho gọn, &amp;gt; 10k rows BẮT BUỘC streaming." style="rounded=1;arcSize=8;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fffbeb;strokeColor=#ca8a04;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=13;fontColor=#0F172A;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=15;spacingRight=15;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
